22", "answer_pdf_sha1": "16ca7e0abba6", "flags": ["needs_image"], "parse_confidence": 0.85, "original_question_number": 7, "raw_text": "7.   如圖 ( 二 )，坐標平面上直線 L 的方程式為 x = −5，\n     直線 M 的方程式為 y = − 3 ，P 點的坐標為 ( a , b ) 。\n     根據圖 ( 二 ) 中 P 點位置判斷，下列關係何者正確？\n     (A) a < − 5 ，b > − 3\n     (B) a < − 5 ，b < − 3\n     (C) a > − 5 ，b > − 3\n     (D) a > − 5 ，b < − 3\n                                                   圖(二)\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": false, "auto_gradable": false, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-112-math-008", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-math", "paper_id": "cap-112-math", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "如圖 ( 三 )，梯形 ABCD 中，AD // BC。若 ∠ ADC = 140°，且 BD ⊥ CD，\n則 ∠ DBC 的度數為何？                         A    D", "options": ["30", "40", "50                                    B           C (D) 60                                        圖(三)", ""], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c426053cd722", "answer_pdf_sha1": "16ca7e0abba6", "flags": ["needs_image", "option_incomplete"], "parse_confidence": 0.6, "original_question_number": 8, "raw_text": "8.   如圖 ( 三 )，梯形 ABCD 中，AD // BC。若 ∠ ADC = 140°，且 BD ⊥ CD，\n     則 ∠ DBC 的度數為何？                         A    D\n     (A) 30\n     (B) 40\n     (C) 50                                    B           C\n     (D) 60                                        圖(三)\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": false, "auto_gradable": false, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-112-math-009", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-math", "paper_id": "cap-112-math", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "有多少個正整數是 18 的倍數，同時也是 216 的因數？", "options": ["2", "6", "10", "12"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null,